TMX Group Gets Bid From Group of Pension Funds, Banks to Counter LSE Offer

-- B y   D a n   H a r t
-- 
2011-05-14T16:59:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-14/tmx-group-gets-bid-from-group-of-pension-funds-banks-to-counter-lse-offer.html
TMX Group Inc. (X) , the Toronto Stock
Exchange owner that’s seeking to combine with  London Stock
Exchange Group Plc (LSE) , said it has received a written acquisition
offer from Maple Group Acquisition Corp.  The offer proposes a combination of cash and stock at a
planned premium to TMX Group’s current price, the company said
in a Canadian Newswire statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Hart at 
 dahart@bloomberg.net  